::GoldenEye::
She lands next to Tail.  She stands infront of Tails.
She hears the voice say Show Yourself.

"It is I, GoldenEye, Predacon. Who are you?"
She turned her head to Tail and whispered,"Don't talk at all, let me 
handle this."

> ::Mosquitor::
> 
> Mosquitor freezes as he hears the bushes rustle behind him, the 
dumb bug 
> frowning. He turns around, taking a few steps toward the source of 
the 
> ruffling. Holding his gun ready, he carefully aproaches Tails' 
location.
> 
> "Show yourself!" he says, ready to kill.
